<html>
  <head>
    <title>E-Ticket Delivery</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0
      auto; padding: 20px; } .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; } .message { margin-bottom:
      20px; } .ticket-details { background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; } .qr-code-list
      { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 20px 0; } .qr-code-list li { margin: 10px; } .ticket {
      margin-top: 2rem; } .ticket img { width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: auto; display: block; } .ticket
      h2 { margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>E-Ticket Delivery</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='message'>
        <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for your purchase. We are pleased to provide you with the following e-tickets:</p>
      </div>
      <div class='ticket-details'>
        <h3>Event Details</h3>
        <p><strong>Event:</strong> {{eventName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{startDate}}</p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
        <p><strong>Ticket Type:</strong> {{ticketType}}</p>
        <p><strong>Quantity:</strong> {{quantity}}</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p>Below are your unique QR codes. Please present these codes to our staff upon arrival at the event:</p>

        <ul class='qr-code-list'>
          {{#each qrCodes}}
            <div class='ticket'>
              <h2>E-Ticket {{this.position}}</h2>
              <img src='cid:{{this.cid}}' />
            </div>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class='message'>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing our services.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Eventopia</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>